snippet.title: Crow-Sourcing Basic Gameplay Example
snippet.description: Since I don't have a streaming audience, the crows were dummy-calls generated by the game itself. However, I have confirmed that Twitch connection works, and when dummies are not being used, each Twitch chat member appears as a crow instance when they submit a want/vote.
